\par\pard\plain \tx720\li720\fi-360\qj\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24 4.\tab The conquest and triumph over the conflict (vv. 16}{\f0\fs24\super c}{\f0\fs24 \endash 21).}
\par\pard\plain \fi360\sb180\qj\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24 Please note: this conflict between Ishmael and Isaac and between their mothers, Hagar and Sarah, is used as an illustration in the New Testament. (See outline and notes\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 Ga. 4:21\endash 31 for discussion.) The conflict pictures the conflict of \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8230\'85}
